article_title: UU church marks 150 years of activist spirit
article_text:
Rochester, MN (55903)

Today

Thunderstorms likely this morning. Then the chance of scattered thunderstorms this afternoon. High around 75F. Winds SSE at 10 to 15 mph. Chance of rain 80%..

Tonight

Scattered thunderstorms this evening becoming more widespread overnight. A few storms may be severe. Low 63F. Winds SE at 5 to 10 mph. Chance of rain 80%.

article_metadata.author: Matthew Stolle, mstolle@postbulletin.com

og.description: When the First Unitarian Universalist Church of Rochester was founded 150 years ago, it was only eight years after Minnesota became a state.
